=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<ol>\n<li>由主acceptor分配到其他reactor去处理</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"nio其他功能\"><a href=\"#nio%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>nio其他功能</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>支持每个reactor包含多个selectors</li>\n<li>文件转移。自动化从文件到网络或网络到文件的拷贝</li>\n<li>内存文件映射。利用<code class=\"language-text\">buffers</code>来处理文件</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Direct buffers</code>。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>支持零拷贝；</li>\n<li>在开启或结束时有开销；</li>\n<li>用于长连接。</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>","timeToRead":2,"frontmatter":{"title":"java nio selector","date":"October 26, 2020","spoiler":"reactor模型"},"fields":{"slug":"/java-nio/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/java-nio/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/go-assembly/","directoryName":"go-assembly"},"frontmatter":{"title":"plan9 assembly 完全解析【转】"}},"next":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["336482444"]}